Description: Unofficial Tapo API Client for TP-Link smart devices
 Tapo is an unofficial API client for TP-Link Tapo smart devices.
 It works with various smart devices including:
 .
  * Light bulbs (L510, L520, L530, L535, L610, L630)
  * Light strips (L900, L920, L930)  
  * Smart plugs (P100, P105, P110, P110M, P115)
  * Power strips (P300, P304M, P316M)
  * Hubs (H100)
  * Switches (S200B)
  * Sensors (KE100, T100, T110, T300, T310, T315)
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 bindings for the Tapo API client,
 which is implemented in Rust for performance and reliability.
